  "text": "The optimal mixing parameter thus induces a shift in the eigenvalues so that the magnitudes of the second-largest and smallest eigenvalues of are balanced. A similar effect is observed in the optimization conducted in [CITATION_1] . It should be noted however, that even with the optimal choice of the proposed algorithm for case cannot outperform global optimization proposed in [CITATION_2] .",
